### API Testing Collection for Gymtec ERP
### Use with Thunder Client or REST Client extension

### Authentication
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

### Get All Clients (Authenticated)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/clients
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get Client by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/clients/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create New Client
POST http://localhost:3000/api/clients
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Gimnasio Test",
  "contact_person": "Juan Pérez",
  "email": "test@example.com", 
  "phone": "+56987654321",
  "rut": "12345678-9",
  "address": "Av. Test 123, Santiago"
}

###

### Get Equipment by Client
GET http://localhost:3000/api/clients/1/equipment
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get All Tickets
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tickets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get Ticket Detail
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tickets/1/detail
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create New Ticket
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tickets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Mantenimiento preventivo",
  "description": "Revisión general del equipo",
  "equipment_id": 1,
  "priority": "Media",
  "type": "Mantenimiento"
}

###

### Update Ticket Status
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/tickets/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "En Progreso"
}

###

### Get Dashboard KPIs
GET http://localhost:3000/api/dashboard/kpis
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get Equipment Models
GET http://localhost:3000/api/models
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create Equipment Model
POST http://localhost:3000/api/models
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Cinta Profesional X1",
  "brand": "TechFit",
  "category": "Cardio",
  "description": "Cinta profesional para gimnasio"
}

###

### Get Users
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Database Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Test Database Connection
GET http://localhost:3000/api/test-connection
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
